Package: kalshiR
Title: R Interface to the Kalshi Prediction Market API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", email = "your@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a tidy R interface to the Kalshi Exchange API
    (https://kalshi.com). Supports authenticated and unauthenticated access
    to market data, historical data, portfolio management, and order
    execution. Returns results as tibbles for easy use with tidyverse
    workflows. Covers series, events, markets, orderbooks, candlesticks,
    fills, positions, and order management.
